data.description: NEW VINYL PLANK FLOORING INSTALLED ** 3/2MH w/wood burning fireplace on 1.11 acres tucked in a private setting with no through traffic. Just a short drive to High Springs/Alachua and Lake City. Columbia County taxes make it worth the short drive over and out of Alachua county. Move in ready! The floor plan features open living area with gas fireplace and built-in cabinets, a kitchen with over sized island/bar, stainless steel appliances and master bathroom with double sinks, garden tub and separate shower. There is a nice barn style shed that can be used for extra storage, lawn equipment or even converted to a workshop or she-shed. The 1.11 acre lot has plenty of room and sunshine for pets, gardening, outdoor entertaining and dark skies at night to see the stars and planets.Land is high and dry, flat, fully fenced. Ready for new owner to love living in the convenient country setting.
